At West Coast Pits, we're not just purebreds; we're a legacy. Our pack stands out with its distinctive look and style—muscular, beautiful, and intelligent. A loving pet or a top-performing show dogs, our dogs offer a unique blend of quality and companionship that sets them apart from the rest.

QUESTIONS?

With a strong champion and grand champion background, our dogs are perfect for working, showing, and families! We are proud to have a distinctive look and style, with muscular, beautiful, and intelligent dogs. ​ Our dogs have their roots in the Hemphill/Wallace foundation breedings between 'Red Brava' and Purple Ribbon 'Hazard Joe.' At West Coast Pits, you won't find just any ordinary pit bulls. You'll see the difference in our dogs, with a unique look and consistency that sets them apart from other breeders. Whether you're looking for a new pet or a top-performing show dog, we have the history and quality to deliver the best.
